.TH KWINCTMCTL 1 "July 2026" "kwin-ctm-monitor 0.1.2" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
kwinctmctl \- manage per-output SDR color transformation matrices in KWin
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B kwinctmctl list
.br
.B kwinctmctl show
.I output
.br
.B kwinctmctl set
.I output m11 m12 m13 m21 m22 m23 m31 m32 m33
.RI [ --timeout seconds ]
.RI [ --force ]
.br
.B kwinctmctl reset
.I output
.SH DESCRIPTION
kwinctmctl addresses an output by connector name or UUID and calls the patched
KWin D-Bus API. A set operation is temporary until confirmed. KWin owns the
timeout and restores the previous matrix if the client exits or confirmation
does not arrive.
.PP
The matrix is applied only to SDR output. KWin suspends it while HDR is active
and restores it when the output returns to SDR.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI --timeout " seconds"
Rollback timeout. The default is 15 seconds.
.TP
.B --force
Confirm immediately without an interactive prompt.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR kwin-ctm-monitor (1)
